      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in museum-quality condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rod bearings have been replaced with high-performance treated shells as preventative maintenance. The chassis remains structurally flawless with a fully reinforced rear subframe. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip M-variable differential. The suspension geometry is optimized via refreshed bushings and factory-correct dampers, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution remains communicative. Finished in original factory paint with zero oxidation, this is a concours-level example for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Zero accidents. Full service records. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 49000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
