    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be listing my pride and joy. This car is in truly stunning, showroom-level condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just drove off the lot for the first time! I've taken incredible care of it, keeping it garaged and spotless, and it's been maintained to perfection. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new and ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have!",
      "price": 44500.0,
