    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is an exceptional example of high-revving naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the iconic S54 straight-six power plant with flawless VANOS timing and individual throttle bodies. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, providing visceral mechanical feedback. This specimen boasts a structurally reinforced subframe, pristine rod bearings, and a suspension tuned for neutral handling and high-speed stability. With zero fluid weeping and perfect compression, this concours-ready chassis represents the zenith of the analog driving era.",
